{"tid":1785511,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【1823】又發現TVB僭建物","createTime":"2019-12-16T12:04:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T19:16:57.000Z","uid":113074,"like":574,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":112,"replies":[{"pid":"da23abb1739b92d570e1fb9a284ac022fda51e9e","tid":1785511,"uid":113074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T12:04:37.000Z","msg":"痴鳩線<br />\ntvb bloody 係僭建物<br />\n連個大台招牌都係僭建物<br />\n屋宇署係唔係又選擇性執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁撚大舊招牌砸落嚟死人點算<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BAMBYfd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBAMBYfd.jpg&h=8b432277&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先生／女士：<br />\n<br />\n主旨:有關TVB外牆巨型招牌僭建物事宜  (檔案編號：xxx)<br />\n<br />\n就你於2019年10月31日的個案，屋宇署的回覆如下：<br />\n<br />\n「屋宇署招牌監管組已派員到上址視察，發現有關的招牌沒有明顯危險，亦無影響樓宇的結構安全，本署已發信予招牌擁有人，<span style=\"color: red;\">敦促其盡早自行安排清拆有關招牌，並將考慮向招牌擁有人發出清拆命令。」</span><br />\n<br />\n如有任何查詢，歡迎與我們的職員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n1823<br />\n客戶服務主任<br />\n林妙娜謹覆 <br />\n2019年12月16日<br />\n<br />\n電話: 1823<br />\n傳真: 2760 1823<br />\n電郵: tellme@1823.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n服務聲明: <a href=\"http://www.1823.gov.hk/di.shtm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.1823.gov.hk%2Fdi.shtm&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7qooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=d99cade1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.1823.gov.hk/di.shtm</a>"},{"pid":"2e3420f99956f2a9709486b340690d093522cd66","tid":1785511,"uid":261873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T12:06:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6c391b776069fe0a35723ea6c72e160737a1ff","tid":1785511,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T12:06:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"af0e7d3023caaa7695a68c8315c43c2795298528","tid":1785511,"uid":165683,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T12:06:53.000Z","msg":"其實可唔可以請Compliance Company 去check"},{"pid":"92ffb3b36471eb886e942974ed941b5b845d913b","tid":1785511,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T12:07:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2322fb926d1220b7c1e25e57df2c77ae68cac72","tid":1785511,"uid":224741,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T12:08:30.000Z","msg":"邊個個想搞法律over my dead body"},{"pid":"e9beeaa137c7275bf5c1c59ae44d0f2ed829b116","tid":1785511,"uid":113074,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T12:13:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bd.gov.hk/tc/building-works/signboards/index_signboards_notice.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fbuilding-works%2Fsignboards%2Findex_signboards_notice.html&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7qooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=9ec49b00\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bd.gov.hk/tc/building-works/signboards/index_signboards_notice.html</a><br />\n<br />\n屋宇署就嚴重違規的超大型招牌採取迅速及大力度的執法行動<br />\n分享<br />\n屋宇署近月積極按《建築物條例》第24B條，向法庭申請優先拆卸令，隨後委派承建商盡快拆除一些嚴重違規及對公眾安全構成很高風險的超大型招牌，以確保公眾安全，並向招牌擁有人收回工程費和附加費。<br />\n<br />\n係唔係tvb就可以豁免清拆令呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef884fac3b70052f31fd32140b83a50576a01547","tid":1785511,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T12:13:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"874a2bba924c231dcdf8138545d0014a248609f4","tid":1785511,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T12:13:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"15f85ee8e16637751adcfe96f176d606a23a908b","tid":1785511,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T12:13:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cbd441351b4cf52e25352a7d9c05f8630af952ff","tid":1785511,"uid":146285,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T12:14:21.000Z","msg":"拆左佢<img s